{"tid":1558042,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消防見死不救  ！！！","createTime":"2019-09-10T10:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T10:04:08.000Z","uid":319452,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f28556b3b8bb5d9a2e1d53fec62f29a371e6eefd","tid":1558042,"uid":319452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:29:00.000Z","msg":"我又quote下同一巴打原post內容啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ahaNAqU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ahaNAqU</a><br />\n<br />\n原post ： <br />\n推斷: 其實消防一早到左，而當時第一個及第二個懷疑失蹤者根本仲清醒行得走得。係消防到左後佢地先俾人懷疑打死同嚇死，消防係月台內都見死不救。直至11:30先開始數人。大膽假設佢地喺係11:10至11:30期間出事，所以消防先話11:30開始進入及數人。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n義士開始被打時係記者走哂之後, 得返黑警 港鐵員工 同 消防丫！！！！！！！！<br />\n你屌得港鐵同謀合污, 咁消防呢？<br />\n消防今次係見死不救加夾口供！！！！！！！<br />\n831記者會女義士話嘔白泡義士被打至少半個鐘，即係消防在場啦..........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">見死不救 !!!!!!!睇黑警打完就拖走！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f957a8e9b4d63cc232dd11ff28332afeb2725298","tid":1558042,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:29:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a01592c8022468a1845fede53248a42fd1794e3","tid":1558042,"uid":319452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:29:44.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"bc978dca347a411a91c5ef83fda87156997f0e30","tid":1558042,"uid":67090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"呢個說法好難令人信服<br />\n唔認為消防會睇住佢地打死人"},{"pid":"eb8be787f927607a7a76c3773459c1c688e9efc0","tid":1558042,"uid":319452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a72ed8f5664120e09d320b2bd63f77f8eca889b","tid":1558042,"uid":319452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fc74bee48e3d7986